On this rooftop where I spoke to Chito that day, I once again think of them and my heart trembles. [l][r]
But it was different from that day. The sky was a clear blue. It was a hatefully clear, sunny day, as if it was blessing the two of them on their journey. [l][r]
[r] I looked up at the sky, took a deep breath, and then spoke into the phone again.[r]
[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

