"What did you name it?" [l][r]
"Eh...?" [l][r]
"Your children. Oh, I'm sorry I'm late in sending you a gift. Twin girls? Congratulations. I have to take good care of my wife." [l][r]
"Ah... yes." [l][r]
"You're going to be a father, right? So, what are their names? [l] You're not going to tell me they're Chito and Yuri, are you?" [l][r]
"No, not at all.
...I mean, those two are probably still on their journey, aren't they?"[l][r]
"Yes, I'm sure of it." [r]
"Yes..." [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

