As I listened to Kanazawa's voice, I suddenly found myself closing my eyes. [l][r]
A dry wind blows on the rooftop and stirs my hair
[l][r]
[r]On the phone was the voice of someone who had once experienced the same despair. [l][r]
It felt like the last remnants to me. A lingering scent of that grey world.
[_tb_end_text]

